Summary: 
Act I:
Sona is found off the coast of Kor. Inn-keeper speaks to Swain. Cole returns from his rounds while fending off the Drogg.
Cole and Sona escape N-rok and flee to meet Garen. Garen agrees to helping Sona and asks Cole to join him. 
End Act I.

Act II:
Cole leaves for Kor. 
Kor is in flames and Cole finds Saul dying. Cole meets Tifa and they venture off towards the mountains. In the mountains they find
the Ancient Druid Sylla. Sylla guides them to the City of Kael-Thoes. Cole and Tifa Speak to the Elders Tribunal. 
End Act II.
